N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 317.1 - Statement of purpose

State Regulations

To establish application procedures, qualifications and
responsibilities for any group of employers which desires to become, or which
has been approved to operate as, a group self-insurer. Notes
